<style>
h3 {
    clear: both;
}
img {
    border:  1px solid #CDCDCD;
}
div.content {
    width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto 0 auto;
}
div.thumb {
    float: left;
    margin: 0 15px 20px 0;
}
</style>

<div class="content">

    <h3>Rasterize Twig extension demo</h3>
    <p>The first time the script loads the images take some seconds to load, then the page reloads very fast because the images are cached for 5 minutes.</p>
    <p>These are the websites of some of the technologies used here:</p>

    <div class="thumb">
        <b>http://php.net</b><br/>
        {{rasterize("http://php.net", 240, 180)}}
    </div>

    <div class="thumb">
        <b>http://symfony.com</b><br/>
        {{rasterize("http://symfony.com", 240, 180)}}
    </div>

    <div class="thumb">
        <b>http://phantomjs.org</b><br/>
        {{rasterize("http://phantomjs.org", 240, 180)}}
    </div>

    <div class="thumb">
        <b>http://twig.sensiolabs.org/</b><br/>
        {{rasterize("http://twig.sensiolabs.org/", 240, 180)}}
    </div>

    <h3>The same using LiipImagineBundle</h3>

    <div class="thumb"><img src="{{ 'http://php.net' | imagine_filter('rasterize') }}" /></div>
    <div class="thumb"><img src="{{ 'http://symfony.com' | imagine_filter('rasterize') }}" /></div>
    <div class="thumb"><img src="{{ 'http://phantomjs.org' | imagine_filter('rasterize') }}" /></div>
    <div class="thumb"><img src="{{ 'http://twig.sensiolabs.org/' | imagine_filter('rasterize') }}" /></div>
</div>


